{"tid":2307764,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有事都做到世界冠軍]七屆一級方程式冠軍咸美頓確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T17:56:59.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02407cf7bb02eff5547f64da4bb8206c3f2f0681","tid":2307764,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562986-20201201.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562986-20201201.htm&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0rXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=45037b9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562986-20201201.htm&h=47c95e41\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562986-20201201.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n七屆一級方程式賽車冠軍、英國車手咸美頓，確診新型肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n一級方程式賽會宣布咸美頓確診的消息，表示咸美頓對新冠病毒檢測呈陽性，將會缺席今個周末在巴林舉行的第二場賽事。<br />\n<br />\n賽會表示，已經提前贏得今屆賽事總冠軍的咸美頓，上星期進行過三次檢測，最後一次在星期日下午進行，結果都是陰性，不過，到星期一早上，咸美頓感到有輕微徵狀，反覆檢測結果亦是陽性，目前正接受治療，並在巴林進行隔離，暫時未知咸美頓能否參與本月11至13日在阿布扎比舉行今個賽季的最後一場賽事。<br />\n<br />\n咸美頓所屬的平治車隊表示，咸美頓情況良好，所有與咸美頓有密切接觸的人士都要進行檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/bf7/cd6/bf7cd6de904eb14238cb0a73501d8aeb7b3a35bf_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fbf7%2Fcd6%2Fbf7cd6de904eb14238cb0a73501d8aeb7b3a35bf_b.jpg&h=4631950d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b3cddb5a1fb56157ce3bfe32dbfd2358e129fd","tid":2307764,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:43:53.000Z","msg":"一陣成隊Mercedes收皮就搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9604851368903046c8117f56923b3113a4c72342","tid":2307764,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"軍已冠理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bafc4c596fa4d65153531186a743aac319592a1","tid":2307764,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"I am ready I am ready"},{"pid":"9a3fbc712ac3af0f78c19479cf28fde233e5c95b","tid":2307764,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}